properties.Name: Westgate Punt Ferry
properties.description: The ferry service runs every 20 minutes on weekdays between 6.30am and 9.20am, and between 4pm and 6.50pm.The fare is $2 one way on weekdays. On weekends and public holidays, the Westgate Punt runs between 9am and 5pm, with crossings at a regular on-demand basis. The fare is $5 one way, or $7 return, on weekends .    http://ptv.vic.gov.au/getting-around/westgate-punt/

properties.Name: Lysterfield Park Mountain Bike Trails
properties.description: The extensive network of tracks around Lysterfield Park were the site of the 2006 Commonwealth Games mountain biking events, and are justly popular.
